  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK257">
<l>uṇṇāmai vēṇṭum pulālaip piṟitoṉṟiṉ</l>
<l>puṇṇa tuṇarvārp peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If men should come to know that flesh is nothing but the unclean ulcer of a body, let them abstain from eating it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
